---
layout: columns.njk
title: Blogroll
permalink: /blogroll/
---

<aside class="columns-rail">
  <h2>Sources</h2>
  <ul>
    {%- for entry in blogroll %}
    <li><a href="{{ entry.url }}">{{ entry.name }}</a></li>
    {%- endfor %}
  </ul>
</aside>

<div class="columns-main">
  <h1>Blogs and sites I enjoy reading</h1>

  <p>Curating and getting into the habit of checking a blogroll has been a really
  useful substitute for high-fructose corn syrup social media consumption.</p>

  {% if blogrollPosts.length %}
  <h2>Recent posts</h2>
  <ul class="blogroll-posts">
    {%- for post in blogrollPosts %}
    <li>
      <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.title }}</a>
      <span class="blogroll-meta">— {{ post.source }}, {{ post.date | readableDate }}</span>
    </li>
    {%- endfor %}
  </ul>
  {% endif %}
</div>
